org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML

Interface EngineSystem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ActuatorSystem, CyberPhysicalSystem, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RoboticSystem, System
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EngineSystemImpl

    public interface EngineSystem
extends ActuatorSystem
    A representation of the model object 'Engine System'. This is the motorization system focused in the engine of a robotic vehicle.

    The following features are supported:

    • Vehicle Traction
    • Max Engine Force
    • Max Breaking Force
    • Max Allowed Steering
    • Max Allowed Velocity
    • Gear ration

    See Also:
    RobotMLPackage.getEngineSystem()
